    - key: dialogue.village.oldman.001.0
      value: Hello, {playerName}. Are you really going into the <color=red>forbidden
        land</color>?
    - key: dialogue.village.oldman.001.1
      value: Wind passes the wooden sign at the village gate, and the old bell rings
        softly.
    - key: dialogue.village.oldman.001.2
      value: If this is fate testing me, I should at least make sure the dialogue
        system works.
    - key: dialogue.village.oldman.001.3
      value: 'System: This dialogue comes from DialogueTable and can be refreshed
        by the Excel importer.'
    - key: dialogue.village.oldman.accept.0
      value: Wonderful. Please find the necklace near the cottage by the forest.
    - key: dialogue.village.oldman.decline.0
      value: I understand. Come back if you change your mind.
    - key: dialogue.village.oldman.reward.0
      value: I will give you 50 coins and a village pass.
    - key: dialogue.village.oldman.persuade.0
      value: Your words reassure me. Fine, I will pay half in advance.
    - key: dialogue.village.oldman.progress.0
      value: The necklace should still be near the cottage by the forest. Come back
        once you find it.
    - key: dialogue.village.oldman.found.0
      value: You found the old necklace beside the cottage. Now you can bring it
        back to the village elder.
    - key: dialogue.village.oldman.complete.0
      value: Yes, this is the necklace. Thank you. I will remember what you did for
        us.
    - key: dialogue.village.oldman.completed.0
      value: You already brought the necklace back. If you need the village's help,
        just ask.
    - key: dialogue.village.oldman.001.option.accept
      value: Of course.
    - key: dialogue.village.oldman.001.option.decline
      value: I do not have time.
    - key: dialogue.village.oldman.001.option.reward
      value: Tell me the reward first.
    - key: dialogue.village.oldman.001.option.persuade
      value: '[Charm 5] Persuade him'
    - key: dialogue.village.oldman.001.option.progress
      value: I have not found the necklace yet.
    - key: dialogue.village.oldman.001.option.find
      value: 'Simulate: find the necklace'
    - key: dialogue.village.oldman.001.option.turnin
      value: Give the necklace to the elder.
    - key: dialogue.village.oldman.001.option.completed
      value: Ask after completing the quest.
    - key: dialogue.shopkeeper.001.0
      value: Welcome. Apples are only <b>3</b> coins today.
    - key: dialogue.shopkeeper.001.1
      value: Bring me {specialItem}, and I can give you a special discount.
    - key: dialogue.tutorial.save.001.0
      value: 'System: Click Save to write the current save slot.'
    - key: dialogue.tutorial.save.001.1
      value: 'System: Click Load to restore data from the current slot.'
    - key: dialogue.tutorial.dialogue.001.0
      value: This line tests auto-play, skip, and Ctrl fast display.
    - key: dialogue.tutorial.dialogue.001.1
      value: 'Rich text also types correctly: <color=#66ccff>blue note</color>, <b>bold
        note</b>.'
    - key: dialogue.template_dialogue_accept.1
      value: 
    - key: dialogue.new_dialogue_001.0
      value: 
